"I should have known that you would be here, Mr. Potter." 
"I just wanted to make sure that my child would be safe as he goes to school this year!" Harry exclaimed quietly. 
"But it's much too dangerous for you to be here! Get out, go back to the Ministea!" Dumbledore yelled at him. Dumbledore truly adored
love that Harry had for his children, but Harry also had to know when enough was enough. It was time for him to go back to the ministry.
